'''线粒体脑肌病'''是一种由[[线粒体|线粒体]]的[[代谢|代谢]]缺陷脱引起的[[脑肌病|脑肌病]]，属于[[线粒体疾病|线粒体疾病]]。此病由Luft于1962年首次采用改良戈莫理氏染色法（Gömöri trichrome stain，MGT）发现。<ref>{{cite journal
 | author = Rolf Luft, Denis Ikkos, Genaro Palmieri, Lars Ernster, and Björn Afzelius
 | title = A case of severe hypermetabolism of nonthyroid origin with a defect in the maintenance of mitochondrial respiratory control: a correlated clinical, biochemical, and morphological study
 | journal = Journal of Clinical Investigation
 | volume = 41
 | issue = 9
 | pages = 1776-1804
 | doi = 10.1172/JCI104637
 | pmid = 14467237
 | url = http://www.mendeley.com/research/a-case-of-severe-hypermetabolism-of-nonthyroid-origin-a-defect-in-the-maintenance-of-mitochondrial-respirtatory-control-a-correlated-clinical-biocehmical-and-morphological-study/
 | language = en
 | date = Sep 1962
 }}{{Dead link|date=2019年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>在[[活体检查|活体检查]]中，[[患者|患者]]的[[肌肉|肌肉]][[组织_(生物学)|组织]]中带有破碎红纤维（或不整红边纤维，raggedredfiber，RRF）。这种线粒体疾病也可同时累及[[中枢神经系统|中枢神经系统]]引起多种[[线粒体肌病|线粒体肌病]]。

== 分型 ==
