 | title = Mitochondrial encephalomyopathy: variable clinical expression within a single kindred
 | journal = Journal of Neurology, Neurosurgery & Psychiatry
 | volume = 56
 | issue = 8
 | pages = 900-905
 | pmid = 8350109
 | pmc = 1015147
 | doi = 10.1136/jnnp.56.8.900
 | url = http://jnnp.bmj.com/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=8350109
 | language = en |date=Aug 1993}}</ref>但在[[医学主题词表|医学主题词表]]（Medical Subject Headings，MeSH）中未将KSS综合征收录到该疾病分类中。

